column3: If you wish to participate in the military exercises, you have come to the right place.
We're taking registrations for the military exercises over in Ul'dah. If you've a mind to participate, you need but say the word.
We are accepting registrations on the Immortal Flames' behalf for the military exercises in Ul'dah. Will you be joining the fray?
If you wish to register for the military exercises, I'm afraid I must disappoint. We require a little more experience of our participants.
In order to access <Sheet(ContentFinderCondition,IntegerParameter(1),43)/>, you must first unlock <Sheet(ContentFinderCondition,IntegerParameter(2),43)/>.
This can be done by making sufficient progress in the quest “It's Probably Pirates.”
